    <li>Pacific parrotlet</li>
    <li>Forpus</li>
    <li>Green-rumped parrotlet</li>
    <li>Yellow-faced parrotlet</li>
    <li>Spectacled parrotlet</li>
    <li>Mexican parrotlet</li>
    <li>Dusky-billed parrotlet</li>
    <li>Touit</li>
    <li>Riparian parrotlet</li>
    <li>Nannopsittaca</li>
    <li>Red-fronted parrotlet</li>
    </ul>
